  (109, 30, 7, 'practice_page', 'Fangda''s Administrative Law Enforcement and Litigation team helps companies communicate with government agencies on regulatory issues, respond to administrative inspections and investigations, manage crises, and represent clients in administrative hearings, reconsideration and litigation procedures, and the team includes former member of the Committee of Administrative Reconsiderations and former regulators.', 'Our team includes highly-regarded former member of the Committee of Administrative Reconsiderations and former regulators, who have unique insights into administrative enforcement measures.', 'https://www.fangdalaw.com/en/bussiness/index26.html'),
  (110, 32, 7, 'practice_page', 'Teneo has an unmatched depth of experience supporting clients through the highest-profile litigation and enforcement actions in the world, beginning with pre-event preparedness and lasting through ongoing issue management, resolution of the matter, and rebuilding post-resolution.', 'Teneo has an unmatched depth of experience supporting clients through the highest-profile litigation and enforcement actions in the world.', 'https://www.teneo.com/service/strategy-communications/litigation-enforcement-action-communications/'),
  (111, 32, 7, 'practice_page', 'Teneo works alongside each client through external and internal inquiries to support transparency and credibility that will protect reputation over the long term, and can make recommendations regarding suggested reforms or organisational restructurings the client can undertake to demonstrate it has emerged from the investigation stronger.', 'Teneo works alongside each client to manage through these external and internal inquiries to support transparency and credibility that will protect reputation over the long term.', 'https://www.teneo.com/service/strategy-communications/litigation-enforcement-action-communications/'),
  (112, 32, 7, 'practice_page', 'Teneo''s crisis communications offering combines the strength of communications, risk and digital teams, and is the only consultancy that can respond to the full suite of needs that a Board or CEO has in a crisis — from initial stages through long-term issues management and eventual reputation rebuilding.', 'Teneo''s integrated crisis offering combines the strength of our communications, risk and digital teams with our dedicated crisis and issues management practice.', 'https://www.teneo.com/service/strategy-communications/investor-relations-and-financial-communications/'),
  (113, 32, 7, 'practice_page', 'Teneo advises companies on their communications and engagement with the investment community during special situations, ensuring securities are valued appropriately within the context of performance and market environment.', 'Teneo''s investor relations strategies allow us to advise companies on their engagement and communications with participants in the global financial markets to ensure that their securities are valued appropriately,', 'https://www.teneo.com/service/strategy-communications/investor-relations-and-financial-communications/'),
  (114, 33, 7, 'practice_page', 'Deloitte China''s Risk, Regulatory & Forensic practice can help organisations build, operate, and sustain right-sized risk and compliance capabilities whether in response to a specific event or planning for the future.', 'We can help you to simplify and accelerate the building, operating and sustaining of right-sized risk and compliance capabilities whether in response to a specific event or planning for the future.', 'https://www.deloitte.com/cn/en/services/consulting/services/risk-regulatory-forensic.html'),
  (115, 33, 7, 'practice_page', 'Deloitte China combines global consistency with local market relevancy and applies meticulous data management, experience with regulatory nuances, and advanced technologies to earn the trust of regulators.', 'Our meticulous approach to data management, experience with regulatory nuances and shrewd application of advanced technologies have earned us the trust of the regulators everywhere.', 'https://www.deloitte.com/cn/en/services/consulting/services/risk-regulatory-forensic.html'),
  (116, 33, 7, 'practice_page', 'Deloitte China helps financial institutions navigate regulatory challenges and reduce financial risk through enhanced data analysis, modelling and risk or finance transformation, building resilient compliance and operational programmes.', 'we work with our clients to navigate these challenges, optimise compliance programmes and reduce financial risk. Together, we build resilient compliance and operational programmes that drive progress', 'https://www.deloitte.com/cn/en/services/consulting/services/risk-regulatory-forensic.html'),
  (117, 34, 8, 'MC-CYB-038', 'Cloudflare WAF''s OWASP Core Ruleset implementation detects XSS attack vectors and can be deployed to block traffic matching those patterns on OWA URL namespaces.', 'Its attack coverage significantly overlaps with Cloudflare Managed Ruleset by detecting common attack vectors such as SQLi and XSS.', 'https://developers.cloudflare.com/waf/get-started/'),
  (118, 34, 8, 'MC-CYB-038', 'Cloudflare WAF checks incoming web and API requests and filters undesired traffic based on sets of rules called rulesets, using the Rules language to filter traffic by request properties such as IP address, URL path, headers, and body content.', 'The Cloudflare Web Application Firewall (Cloudflare WAF) checks incoming web and API requests and filters undesired traffic based on sets of rules called rulesets.', 'https://developers.cloudflare.com/waf/'),
  (119, 35, 8, 'MC-CYB-038', 'F5 BIG-IP Advanced WAF protects apps, APIs, and data against the most prevalent attacks such as zero-day vulnerabilities, app-layer DoS attacks, threat campaigns, application takeover, and bots.', 'Protect your apps, APIs, and data against the most prevalent attacks such as zero-day vulnerabilities, app-layer DoS attacks, threat campaigns, application takeover, and bots.', 'https://www.f5.com/products/big-ip-services/advanced-waf'),
  (120, 35, 8, 'MC-CYB-038', 'BIG-IP Advanced WAF delivers defenses for the OWASP Top 10, defending apps from today''s biggest security concerns including XSS and credential theft.', 'Defenses for the OWASP Top 10. Defends apps from today''s biggest security concerns, including those listed in the OWASP Top 10, including top MCP vulnerabilities.', 'https://www.f5.com/products/big-ip-services/advanced-waf'),
  (121, 35, 8, 'MC-CYB-038', 'BIG-IP Advanced WAF identifies and blocks attacks other WAFs miss using behavioral analytics, layer 7 DoS mitigation, application-layer encryption, and threat intelligence services.', 'BIG-IP Advanced WAF identifies and blocks attacks other WAFs miss. BIG-IP Advanced WAF delivers a dedicated, dynamic dashboard ensuring compliance against threats listed in the OWASP Top 10, guided configurations for common WAF use cases,', 'https://www.f5.com/products/big-ip-services/advanced-waf'),
  (122, 36, 8, 'MC-CYB-017', 'Duo adds two-factor authentication to Outlook Web App (OWA) logins, offering inline user enrollment, self-service device management, and support for a variety of authentication methods — such as passkeys and security keys, Duo Push, or Verified Duo Push — in the Universal Prompt.', 'Duo adds two-factor authentication to Outlook Web App (OWA) logins, offering inline user enrollment, self-service device management, and support for a variety of authentication methods — such as passkeys and security keys, Duo Push,', 'https://duo.com/docs/owa'),
  (123, 36, 8, 'MC-CYB-017', 'Duo for OWA is documented for Exchange Server Subscription Edition running on Windows Server 2019 or newer, with installation on Exchange Server instances running the Exchange Client Access services.', 'These instructions are for Exchange Server Subscription Edition (SE), running on Windows Server 2019 or newer.', 'https://duo.com/docs/owa'),
  (124, 36, 8, 'MC-CYB-017', 'Duo for OWA installs as an IIS module that stops and restarts IIS services on Exchange servers automatically, intercepting the OWA authentication flow to require secondary Duo authentication after primary username and password verification.', 'Install Duo on the Microsoft Exchange Server instances running the Exchange Client Access services. The installation process varies slightly depending on how many Client Access servers you have.', 'https://duo.com/docs/owa'),
  (125, 37, 8, 'MC-CYB-019', 'Splunk''s Threat Research team released an Analytic Story called ''HAFNIUM group'' via Enterprise Security Content Update version 3.16 to provide visibility into adversary actions exploiting Microsoft Exchange zero-days, including detections for W3WP.exe spawning shells and OWA-specific IIS log patterns.', 'the Splunk Threat Research team released an Analytic Story called "HAFNIUM group" via Enterprise Security Content Update version 3.16 on March 8th to provide visibility into these adversary actions.', 'https://www.splunk.com/en_us/blog/security/detecting-microsoft-exchange-vulnerabilities-0-8-days-later.html'),
  (126, 37, 8, 'MC-CYB-019', 'Splunk provides SPL detection searches targeting W3WP.exe (IIS worker process) spawning command shells — the primary Exchange OWA exploitation indicator — using both Sysmon and Windows Security Event Log sources.', 'W3wp.exe Spawning Shell. This query identifies a shell, PowerShell.exe or Cmd.exe, spawning from W3WP.exe, or IIS.', 'https://www.splunk.com/en_us/blog/security/detecting-microsoft-exchange-vulnerabilities-0-8-days-later.html'),
  (127, 37, 8, 'MC-CYB-019', 'Splunk provides Exchange HttpProxy log ingestion guidance and an SPL search targeting the OABVirtualDirectory reset POST pattern in Exchange IIS logs — the specific log signature of the OWA exploit chain.', 'This search is based on the mshttp_proxy sourcetype that we defined earlier. It picks up the reset of the OAB Virtual Directory, which is called out in the Praetorian blog.', 'https://www.splunk.com/en_us/blog/security/detecting-microsoft-exchange-vulnerabilities-0-8-days-later.html'),
  (128, 38, 8, 'MC-CYB-036', 'Rapid7 InsightIDR observed a notable increase in exploitation of Microsoft Exchange through existing detections in InsightIDR''s Attacker Behavior Analytics (ABA), with the Managed Detection and Response team identifying multiple related compromises of on-premises Microsoft Exchange servers with OWA accessible to the public internet.', 'Rapid7 has observed a notable increase in the exploitation of Microsoft Exchange through existing detections in InsightIDR''s Attacker Behavior Analytics (ABA).', 'https://www.rapid7.com/blog/post/2021/03/03/rapid7s-insightidr-enables-detection-and-response-to-microsoft-exchange-0-day/'),
  (129, 38, 8, 'MC-CYB-036', 'Rapid7 InsightIDR provided proactive, actionable steps to customers to thwart Exchange zero-day attacks before Microsoft''s public acknowledgement, with the MDR team identifying attacker techniques, source IPs, and tools used, including detection of webshell uploads to OWA paths.', 'Within a very short period of time, our analysts were able to identify how the attackers were executing commands, where they were coming from, and what tools they were using.', 'https://www.rapid7.com/blog/post/2021/03/03/rapid7s-insightidr-enables-detection-and-response-to-microsoft-exchange-0-day/'),
  (130, 38, 8, 'MC-REG-004', 'Rapid7 InsightVM''s Active Risk scoring incorporates the CISA Known Exploited Vulnerabilities (KEV) catalog alongside AttackerKB, Metasploit, and ExploitDB to provide threat-aware vulnerability risk scores, directly surfacing KEV-listed Exchange vulnerabilities for prioritised remediation.', 'Active Risk uses CVSS scores along with intelligence from threat feeds like AttackerKB, Metasploit, ExploitDB, Project Heisenberg, CISA KEV list,', 'https://www.rapid7.com/blog/post/2023/09/25/introducing-active-risk/'),
  (131, 39, 8, 'MC-REG-016', 'OneTrust Incident & Breach Response enables organisations to centrally manage, analyse, investigate, report and monitor the full incident and breach lifecycle and is powered by Databreachpedia™ Global Law Engine, integrating hundreds of region-specific breach notification laws directly into the platform.', 'OneTrust Incident & Breach Response enables organisations to centrally manage, analyse, investigate, report and monitor the full incident and breach lifecycle and is powered by Databreachpedia™ Global Law Engine,', 'https://www.onetrust.com/news/onetrust-enhances-incident-breach-response/'),
  (132, 39, 8, 'MC-REG-016', 'OneTrust addresses the GDPR Article 33 requirement that controllers notify supervisory authorities within 72 hours of becoming aware of a personal data breach, with the 72-hour notification window built into its automated response workflows.', 'With breach notification laws ranging from 72 hours to more than 30 days, privacy and security teams need a flexible solution to centrally manage response plans across the globe', 'https://www.onetrust.com/news/onetrust-enhances-incident-breach-response/'),
  (133, 39, 8, 'MC-REG-016', 'OneTrust Incident & Breach Response automatically tailors response workflows based on impacted regions'' breach notification laws and can integrate into a company''s SIEM and ITSM tools for automated breach intake.', 'OneTrust Incident & Breach Response helps privacy and security teams manage the full lifecycle of personal data incidents and automatically tailors response workflows based on impacted regions'' breach notification laws.', 'https://www.onetrust.com/news/onetrust-enhances-incident-breach-response/'),
  (134, 40, 8, 'case_study', 'CrowdStrike Falcon Complete detected and disrupted a mass exploitation campaign of Microsoft Exchange Server OWA zero-day vulnerabilities, identifying compromised Exchange application pools via the MSExchangeOWAAppPool process tree, removing webshells, and containing impacted hosts — while the permanent patch was unavailable.', 'OverWatch flagged the "W3WP.EXE" process as malicious due to an observed attempt to exploit the Exchange application pool named "MSExchangeOWAAppPool."', 'https://www.crowdstrike.com/en-us/blog/falcon-complete-stops-microsoft-exchange-server-zero-day-exploits/'),
  (135, 40, 8, 'case_study', 'CrowdStrike IR conducts IIS log forensics, ECP server log analysis, and endpoint activity monitor (EAM) queries to identify the full scope of Exchange OWA exploitation, including webshell file writes and post-exploitation commands executed under W3WP.exe.', 'Falcon Complete immediately began pulling the IIS logs from the impacted hosts to search for artifacts in an attempt to confirm the initial entry vector.', 'https://www.crowdstrike.com/en-us/blog/falcon-complete-stops-microsoft-exchange-server-zero-day-exploits/'),
  (136, 41, 8, 'practice_page', 'Mandiant Incident Response service deploys on-call incident responders to immediately begin triage activities, minimise business impact through methodical investigation and containment, and provide rapid recovery of business operations with full breach remediation.', 'On-call incident responders to immediately begin triage activities - Minimize business impact through methodical investigation and containment - Rapid recovery of business operations with full breach remediation', 'https://cloud.google.com/security/consulting/mandiant-incident-response-services'),
  (137, 41, 8, 'practice_page', 'Mandiant Compromise Assessment searches for previously unseen attacker activity with insight into motivations, identifies weaknesses in configurations and vulnerabilities, and provides best-practice recommendations to effectively respond to future incidents.', 'Search for previously unseen attacker activity with insight into motivations - Identify weaknesses in configurations, vulnerabilities, and policy violations - Best practice recommendations to effectively respond to future incidents', 'https://cloud.google.com/security/consulting/mandiant-incident-response-services'),
  (138, 42, 9, 'MC-ENV-019', 'OSRL''s partnership with Sea Alarm gives members anytime expert wildlife response support, with one advisor deployable onsite and another providing remote technical guidance.', 'OSRL''s partnership with Sea Alarm gives members anytime expert wildlife response support, with one advisor deployable onsite and another providing remote technical guidance.', 'https://www.osrl.com/services/response/wildlife/'),
  (139, 42, 9, 'MC-ENV-019', 'GOWRS delivers an expert-led wildlife assessment in four days, guiding OSRL members on response needs, local capacity, and next steps for full-scale mobilisation.', 'GOWRS delivers an expert-led wildlife assessment in four days, guiding OSRL members on response needs, local capacity, and next steps for full-scale mobilisation.', 'https://www.osrl.com/services/response/wildlife/'),
  (140, 42, 9, 'MC-ENV-020', 'OSRL wildlife services include monitoring wildlife in real-time, prioritising clean-up efforts to prevent oil from reaching sensitive habitats, deterring animals from entering oiled areas, and rehabilitating affected species, with pre-planning and early intervention essential to ensure an effective response.', 'This includes monitoring wildlife in real-time, prioritising clean-up efforts to prevent oil from reaching sensitive habitats, deterring animals from entering oiled areas, and rehabilitating affected species.', 'https://www.osrl.com/services/response/wildlife/'),
  (141, 43, 9, 'MC-ENV-019', 'Sea Alarm has extensive experience in dealing with oiled wildlife emergencies, providing strategic and tactical advice, coaching key individuals, and helping to set up management and information systems when mobilised to a response.', 'Having been involved in the response to a large number of oil spill incidents, Sea Alarm has extensive experience in dealing with oiled wildlife emergencies.', 'https://www.sea-alarm.org/our-work/response/'),
  (142, 43, 9, 'MC-ENV-019', 'Sea Alarm can assist with the identification, mobilisation and integration of international resources such as experts and equipment, with procedures in place to mobilise the world''s most experienced resources to help professionalise a local response effort.', 'Sea Alarm can assist with the identification, mobilisation and integration of international resources, such as experts and equipment.', 'https://www.sea-alarm.org/our-work/response/'),
