  (144, 44, 9, 'MC-ENV-020', 'International Bird Rescue will mobilise and deploy a trained response team to support the wildlife response including oiled wildlife facility design, set up and operation, overall management of rehabilitation program, veterinary medical evaluation, triage, monitoring and treatment.', 'International Bird Rescue will mobilize and deploy a trained response team to support the wildlife response needs in any of the following areas:

