  (151, 45, 9, 'practice_page', 'CEDRE''s on-site missions include conducting surveys and assessing the situation, taking part in incident management units, drafting technical and strategic recommendations, monitoring clean-up operations, and supporting during the post-spill phase.', 'Conducting surveys and assessing the situation
