  (152, 43, 9, 'practice_page', 'EUROWA is a European network of expert organisations with Sea Alarm as its secretariat, including trained experts that can form a response team mobilisable to assist a local response, with its own stockpile of oiled wildlife response equipment held in Belgium available for any interested party in Europe.', 'EUROWA is a European network of European expert organisations with Sea Alarm as its secretariat. The network includes trained experts that can form a response team that can be mobilised to assist a local response.', 'https://www.sea-alarm.org/our-work/response/'),
